subdefinitions.definition: Subsisting on, or pertaining to, a diet of raw food.
examples: I was 100% raw from 2014 until early 2018.

Unpleasantly cold or damp . ( of weather )
Unmasked , undisguised , strongly expressed . ( of an emotion, personality, etc. )
Candid in a representation of unpleasant facts, conditions, etc.
examples: a raw description of the American political arena
